this is a list of hungarian football transfers for the 2010 summer transfer window by club. only transfers of clubs in the soproni liga and hungarian national championship ii are included. the summer transfer window will open on 1 june 2010, although a few transfers may take place prior to that date. the window will close at midnight on 31 august 2010. players without a club may join one at any time, either during or in between transfer windows.